'''嚴重急性呼吸道綜合症相关冠狀病毒'''（{{lang-en|''Severe acute respiratory syndrome-related coronavirus''}}<!-- 病毒种以下学名皆为英文、且一律斜写-->），簡稱'''SARS相关冠状病毒'''（{{lang|en|SARSr-CoV}}），是[[冠狀病毒科|冠狀病毒科]][[乙型冠状病毒属|乙型冠状病毒属]]的一个[[种|种]]。<ref name="Thiel">{{Cite book|title=Coronaviruses: Molecular and Cellular Biology|url=https://archive.org/details/coronavirusesmol0000unse|last=Thiel V (editor).|publisher=Caister Academic Press|year=2007|isbn=978-1-904455-16-5|edition=1st}}</ref>该种病毒现有2个可传染人的[[分型|分型]]<ref name="ICTV">{{Cite journal|title=The species Severe acute respiratory syndrome-related coronavirus : classifying 2019-nCoV and naming it SARS-CoV-2|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41564-020-0695-z|last=Gorbalenya|first=Alexander E.|last2=Baker|first2=Susan C.|date=2020-04|journal=Nature Microbiology|accessdate=2020-03-03|issue=4|doi=10.1038/s41564-020-0695-z|volume=5|pages=536–544|language=en|issn=2058-5276|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305112708/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41564-020-0695-z|archivedate=2020-03-05|deadurl=no|last3=Baric|first3=Ralph S.|last4=de Groot|first4=Raoul J.|last5=Drosten|first5=Christian|last6=Gulyaeva|first6=Anastasia A.|last7=Haagmans|first7=Bart L.|last8=Lauber|first8=Chris|last9=Leontovich|first9=Andrey M.}}</ref>。

==分型==
* 第一个分型称为[[嚴重急性呼吸道綜合症冠狀病毒|嚴重急性呼吸道綜合症冠狀病毒]]（{{lang-en|''Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus''}}，简称{{lang|en|SARS-CoV}}）<ref name="ICTV" />，发现于2003年，引发了[[嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症|嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症]]的疫情，有可能是通过[[菊頭蝠科|菊头蝠]]传播到人类的<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Discovery of a rich gene pool of bat SARS-related coronaviruses provides new insights into the origin of SARS coronavirus|url=https://dx.plos.org/10.1371/journal.ppat.1006698|last=Hu|first=Ben|last2=Zeng|first2=Lei-Ping|date=2017-11-30|journal=PLOS Pathogens|issue=11|doi=10.1371/journal.ppat.1006698|editor-last=Drosten|editor-first=Christian|volume=13|pages=e1006698|language=en|issn=1553-7374|pmc=PMC5708621|pmid=29190287|last3=Yang|first3=Xing-Lou|last4=Ge|first4=Xing-Yi|last5=Zhang|first5=Wei|last6=Li|first6=Bei|last7=Xie|first7=Jia-Zheng|last8=Shen|first8=Xu-Rui|last9=Zhang|first9=Yun-Zhi|access-date=2021-04-07|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731032614/https://journals.plos.org/plospathogens/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.ppat.1006698|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* 第二个分型称为[[嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症冠狀病毒2型|嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症冠狀病毒2型]]（{{lang-en|''Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2''}}，简称{{lang|en|SARS-CoV-2}}），发现于2019年，引发了[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]的疫情<ref name="ICTV" />，有研究认为，该病毒类型可能是通过[[马来穿山甲|马来穿山甲]]传播给人类的<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Identification of 2019-nCoV related coronaviruses in Malayan pangolins in southern China|url=https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.02.13.945485v1|last=Lam|first=Tommy Tsan-Yuk|last2=Shum|first2=Marcus Ho-Hin|date=2020-02-18|journal=bioRxiv|accessdate=2020-02-20|doi=10.1101/2020.02.13.945485|pages=2020.02.13.945485|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116075736/https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.02.13.945485v1|archivedate=2021-01-16|deadurl=no|last3=Zhu|first3=Hua-Chen|last4=Tong|first4=Yi-Gang|last5=Ni|first5=Xue-Bing|last6=Liao|first6=Yun-Shi|last7=Wei|first7=Wei|last8=Cheung|first8=William Yiu-Man|last9=Li|first9=Wen-Juan}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Viral Metagenomics Revealed Sendai Virus and Coronavirus Infection of Malayan Pangolins (Manis javanica)|url=https://www.mdpi.com/1999-4915/11/11/979|last=Liu|first=Ping|last2=Chen|first2=Wu|date=2019/11|journal=Viruses|accessdate=2020-02-20|issue=11|doi=10.3390/v11110979|volume=11|pages=979|language=en|pmc=PMC6893680|pmid=31652964|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114063145/https://www.mdpi.com/1999-4915/11/11/979|archivedate=2021-01-14|deadurl=no|last3=Chen|first3=Jin-Ping}}</ref>。截至2021年6月，病毒溯源工作仍在进行<ref>{{cite web |title=新冠溯源：世卫要求复查意大利早期样本 |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E6%BA%AF%E6%BA%90%E4%B8%96%E5%8D%AB%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%8D%E6%9F%A5%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%AC/a-57760988 |website=德国之声 |accessdate=2021-06-11 |date=2021-06-02 |archive-date=2021-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210611124740/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E6%BA%AF%E6%BA%90%E4%B8%96%E5%8D%AB%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%8D%E6%9F%A5%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%AC/a-57760988 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。統計至2021年2月4日為止，病例數約為SARS-CoV的12800倍，病逝人數約為2900倍。

